{
  "texts": [
    "Tapadiya et al. [92] demonstrated the Marathi language's system for recognizing weather entities.",
    "They have utilized to forecast the patterns by using CRFs and BiLSTM models.FastText and transformer based mBERT embeddings are utilized to show the word vectors.",
    "The accuracy of the result shown in the Bi-LSTM CRF model with FastText word embedding is 97.45%.",
    "Mundotiya et al. [25] focused on creating a NER benchmark dataset for machine translation systems designed to translate from various languages to Hindi by annotating certain areas of the given corpus with named items.",
    "They used 22 entity tags to annotate Maithali, Magahi and Bhojpuri corpora with sizes of 157,468, 56,190 and 228, 373 tokens respectively."
  ]
}